  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improvement of the periodic reporting mechanisms under the 2003 Convention (199GLO4939)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will improve the periodic mechanism under the 2003 Convention, with three main outcomes:
-	Periodic reporting exercise facilitated for States Parties;
-	Periodic reports information more widely used and disseminated;
-	Periodic Reporting mechanism aligned with the monitoring and evaluation framework of the 2003 Convention.
The main activities will consist of:
-	Online developments to offer a wide range of functionalities in terms of input, visibility and optimization of data collection;
-	Studies and expert meeting on periodic reports and formats;
-	Revision of the formats and Operational Directives.</narrative>
  </description>
